info.author: Zeb Nicholls, Robert Gieseke, Jared Lewis, Sven Willner, Chris Smith
info.description:
OpenSCM-Runner
==============

OpenSCM-Runner is a thin wrapper to run simple climate models with a
unified interface.
At present, it supports emissions driven runs only.
This wrapper is implemented while
`OpenSCM <https://github.com/openscm/openscm>`_ is still a work in
progress.
info.name: openscm-runner
info.summary: Thin wrapper to run simple climate models (emissions driven runs only)
